des:
Are you a huge New England Patriots fan? Then you need the Musket Fire Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on the Patriots. Musket Fire is the New England Patriots news and opinions site brought to you by the FanSided Network. 

Musket Fire is dedicated to providing top-notch Patriots news, views, and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
